Label: Restrictive eating
Description: Restrictive eating: refers to times when you intentionally ate less than appropriate for the situation out of concern for your body shape and/or weight (e.g., eating an apple for dinner, eating a diet frozen meal at a family dinner, or eating only a small salad even if you’re very hungry could be considered restrictive eating). How much did you engage in any of these eating behaviors since waking up this morning? 1 = Not at all, 2 = A little, 3 = somewhat, 4 = Moderately, 5 = Somewhat, 6 = Extremely

Label: Binge eating
Description: Binge eating: refers to times when you have eaten what other people would regard as an unusually large amount of food (given the circumstances) AND had a sense of lost control over your eating.How much did you engage in any of these eating behaviors since waking up this morning?  1 = Not at all, 2 = A little, 3 = somewhat, 4 = Moderately, 5 = Somewhat, 6 = Extremely

Label: Purging
Description: Purging: refers to times when you have done any of the following as a means of controlling your shape or weight: made yourself sick (e.g., vomited), taken laxatives, exercised in a “driven” or “compulsive” way.How much did you engage in any of these eating behaviors since waking up this morning?  1 = Not at all, 2 = A little, 3 = somewhat, 4 = Moderately, 5 = Somewhat, 6 = Extremely
